description: Try our easy to follow Speedy Barramundi & Slaw Bowls recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Bowl,Pescatarian,Low saturated fat,Tree nut free,Mar 2020,Sesame free,Coleslaw,Barramundi,Fish,High protein,High fibre,Tomato,Dinner Made Easy,Peanut free
name: Speedy Barramundi & Slaw Bowls Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180Â°C. Turn 4 x 9cm bowls upside down and spray with oil. Heat wraps as per packet instructions.
Press wraps over bowls. Bake, on baking tray, for 8 minutes. Remove wraps from bowls, turn right-side up and bake for 5 minutes or until golden. Cool.
Pat fish skin dry. Season. Heat 2 tbs oil in a pan. Cook fish, skin-side down, for 2-3 minutes. Turn and cook for 4 minutes. Cool. Flake.
Toss coleslaw with half the dressing from the kit. Fill bowls with slaw, fish and tomato, and feta from the kit. Serve with remaining dressing.
